    <briefdescription>
<para>Abstract interface for file download implementations (e.g., curl-based, libfetch, etc.) </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Plugin implementations must provide a factory function pair that follows this interface. The plugin must export: extern &quot;C&quot; FileDownloadPlugin* CreateFileDownloadPlugin() extern &quot;C&quot; bool InitializePluginFunction(Dali::FileDownloadPlugin*) extern &quot;C&quot; void DestroyFileDownloadPlugin(FileDownloadPlugin* plugin) </para>
